Package: ldccr
Title: Utilities for Various Japanese Corpora
Version: 0.0.6.900
Authors@R: c(
    person("Akiru", "Kato", email = "paithiov909@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Kato Akiru <paithiov909@gmail.com>
Description: The goal of ldccr package is to make easy to use Japanese language resources.
    This package provides parsers for several Japanese corpora that are free or open licensed
    and a downloader of zipped text files published on Aozora Bunko.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/paithiov909/ldccr
BugReports: https://github.com/paithiov909/ldccr/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
